OL,3,CEmma Raducanu pulls out of Wimbledon
OL,4,Cdue to injury
OL,6,FEmma Raducanu has pulled out of
OL,7,FWimbledon on the eve of the grand slam
OL,8,Fdue to a stress fracture in her leg.
OL,10,FThe British number one announced the
OL,11,Fdecision late on Sunday evening, just
OL,12,Fhours after she had reporters she
OL,13,Fplanned to play following speculation
OL,14,Fabout her fitness.
OL,16,FWriting on Instagram, the 23-year-old
OL,17,Fsaid: "I can't believe I'm saying
OL,18,Fthis, but sadly I've had to withdraw
OL,19,Ffrom this year's Wimbledon.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
