CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782703089
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu pulls out of Wimbledon
OL,4,Cdue to injury
OL,6,F"I've done everything possible to try
OL,7,Fto get to the start line tomorrow but
OL,8,Fafter a final scan tonight, the niggle
OL,9,FI've been managing has developed into
OL,10,Fa stress fracture and I've been
OL,11,Fmedically advised to stop pushing
OL,12,Fthrough.
OL,14,F"Playing at Wimbledon, in front of a
OL,15,Fhome crowd, means everything to me, so
OL,16,Fthis is really difficult to process.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
