OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782703089
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu pulls out of Wimbledon
OL,4,Cdue to injury
OL,6,F"I want to thank you all for your
OL,7,Fsupport and encouragement. Especially
OL,8,Fat a time like this, it is invaluable.
OL,9,FI look forward to seeing you when I'm
OL,10,Fback."
OL,12,FRaducanau was due to play Antonia
OL,13,FRuzic on Court One on Monday lunchtime.
OL,15,FConcerns over her fitness were raised
OL,16,Fwhen Raducanu was reportedly spotted
OL,17,Fwearing a protective boot on Wednesday.
