OL,3,CEmma Raducanu pulls out of Wimbledon
OL,4,Cdue to injury
OL,6,FShe did not take to the practice
OL,7,Fcourts until Saturday, when she wore
OL,8,Fstrapping on her lower right leg and
OL,9,Fcut short a session against Russian
OL,10,FAnna Kalinskaya after moving gingerly
OL,11,Fand losing four games in a row.
OL,13,FAll eyes were on Raducanu during her
OL,14,Fsession with hitting partner Alexis
OL,15,FCanter on Sunday morning, and that
OL,16,Fappeared to be more positive, despite
OL,17,Fthe former US Open champion not fully
OL,18,Ftesting out her movement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
