OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782703089
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu pulls out of Wimbledon
OL,4,Cdue to injury
OL,6,F"I'm going to do everything with my
OL,7,Fteam in terms of treatment," said
OL,8,FRaducanu at her press conference,
OL,9,Fwhere she revealed she had been
OL,10,Fbattling the issue since before her
OL,11,Frun to the final at Queen's Club two
OL,12,Fweeks ago.
OL,14,F"That's the plan right now, to play. I
OL,15,Fhave a lower leg niggle that I've been
OL,16,Fdealing with since before Queen's,
OL,17,Factually, from the back end of the
OL,18,Fclay-court season.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@\O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
