FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782703089
OL,3,CEmma Raducanu pulls out of Wimbledon
OL,4,Cdue to injury
OL,6,F"Queen's, during that week, was a lot
OL,7,Fof load for me. Five matches after
OL,8,Fhaving not competed for a while. But
OL,9,FI'm just managing it with my team as
OL,10,Fbest as I possibly can, exhausting all
OL,11,Foptions and doing what we can."
OL,13,FThis will be a bitter blow in what has
OL,14,Fbeen another disrupted year for
OL,15,FRaducanu, who was hampered by a foot
OL,16,Fproblem in pre-season and then
OL,17,Fsidelined for two-and-a-half months
OL,18,Fwith a post-viral illness in the
OL,19,Fspring.
